{"metadata":{"externalID":"c:@E@MLNTextWritingMode@MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","roleHeading":"Enumeration Case","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"case","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal"}],"title":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal"}]},"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal"}]}]},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":null,"code":[" If a text's language supports horizontal writing mode, symbols with point"," placement would be laid out horizontally."]}],"kind":"content"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode"]]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode\/mlntextwritingmodehorizontal"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"sections":[],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode\/MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNTextWritingMode/MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode\/mlntextwritingmodehorizontal","type":"topic","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode\/MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","role":"symbol","title":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"role":"collection","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","title":"MapLibre","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNTextWritingMode":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode","title":"MLNTextWritingMode","abstract":[{"text":"The property allows control over a symbol’s orientation. Note that the property","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"values act as a hint, so that a symbol whose language doesn’t support the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"provided orientation will be laid out in its natural orientation. Example:","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"English point symbol will be rendered horizontally even if array value contains","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"single ‘vertical’ enum value. The order of elements in an array define priority","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"order for the placement of an orientation variant.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingMode","kind":"identifier"}]}}}